Source: libqdrive
Maintainer: Andreas Misje <amisje@gmail.com>
Homepage: http://github.com/misje/libqdrive
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Standards-Version: 3.9.8
Vcs-Git: git://github.com/misje/libqdrive

Package: libqdrive0
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Architecture: any
Description: Qt interface for UDisks2
 This library includes support for enumerating disks and partitions on the
 system, as well as monitoring hotplug events. It also includes a Qt table
 model for partitions, suitable for use in a widget/QML GUI.

Package: libqdrive-dev
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libqdrive0 (= ${binary:Version})
Architecture: any
Description: Qt interface for UDisks2
 This library includes support for enumerating disks and partitions on the
 system, as well as monitoring hotplug events. It also includes a Qt table
 model for partitions, suitable for use in a widget/QML GUI.
